basic.blooming: Flowering period February-May, fruiting period September-October
basic.color: Flower color white, red, fruit color green, yellow, red

maintenance.soil: Peat or soil with specific nutrients
maintenance.sunlight: Like half shade, may grow in places with bright scattered light
maintenance.watering: Water thoroughly when soil is dry, avoid saturated water
maintenance.fertilization: Mainly use base fertilizers, top-dressing at the late stages
maintenance.pruning: Remove dead and diseased branches timely
